$BR
\(x_1 = \) \{ans_rule(5)\} \{ $poptypeS1->menu() \} and $BR
\(x_2 = \) \{ans_rule(5)\} \{ $poptypeS2->menu() \}.$BR$BR

The axis of rotation is \(y=-$c\) which is a \{ $poptypeAR ->menu() \} that is \{ $poptypeARrel ->menu() \} the region. 

